📗
	A route that handles a specific path and method combination, with a callable
	that returns a response.
📗
🐇 🚄 🍇
	🐊 🛣

	📗
		Panics if anything is wrong with the input.
	📗
	🐇🔒❗ 💥 method🔡 path🔡 🍇
		💭 Panic if the method is not a valid HTTP method
		🍿🔤CONNECT🔤🔤DELETE🔤🔤GET🔤🔤HEAD🔤🔤OPTIONS🔤🔤PATCH🔤🔤POST🔤🔤PUT🔤🔤TRACE🔤🍆 ➡ validMethods
		↪ ❎🐦validMethods method❓❗ 🍇
			🤯🐇💻 🔤Method 🧲method🧲 is not a valid HTTP method🔤❗
		🍉
		💭 Panic if the path does not start with a "/"
		↪ ❎🎼path 🔤/🔤❗❗ 🍇
			🤯🐇💻 🔤Path 🧲path🧲 does not start with a "/"🔤❗
		🍉
