	🖍🆕 method🔡
	🖍🆕 path🔡
	🖍🆕 handler🍇📥➡📤🍉

	📗
		A route that handles `httpMethod` requests to `requestPath` with the
		`handler`.
	📗
	🆕 httpMethod🔡 requestPath🔡 🍼handler🍇📥➡📤🍉 🍇
		📫httpMethod❗ ➡ 🖍 method
		📪requestPath❗ ➡ 🖍 path
		💥🐇🚄 method path❗
	🍉

	❓👣 request📥 ➡ 👌 🍇
		↩ 🚇request❓ 🙌 method 🤝 🛤request❓ 🙌 path
	🍉

	❗👣 request📥 ➡ 📤 🍇
		↩ ⁉handler request❗
